'''The Force Is With Them: The Legacy of Star Wars''' is a featurette produced by [[Gary Leva]] that was included in the [[2004]] DVD box set of the ''Star Wars'' [[Original trilogy]]. It explained the cultural impact ''Star Wars'' had on the world and how it changed the lives of the actors involved.

